item.description:
The Rochester 912 Group is hosting a set of debates the first is between Senatorial hopefuls, Kelly Ayotte, Jim Bender, Bill Binnie, Ken Blevens and Ovide Lamontagne. These debates will be open to all Rochester 912 Group members and the public. We are allowing 2 hours for the first set of debates. I asked Jeff Chidester to moderate the event. We will also have one media person on the panel and myself. Please submit your questions at the next 912 meeting on April 12th to Sue or me. I will give a bit of the rundown on the event at that time.
This is your event Rochester 912r's.
Semper Fi,
Jerry
item.name: Rochester 912 Group Senatorial Debates
